Responsive Design Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides responsive design system for mobile applications.
Implements breakpoint-based layouts, flexible grids, and adaptive sizing
for different screen sizes and orientations on mobile devices.

Key Features:
- Breakpoint-based responsive design
- Flexible grid systems
- Adaptive component sizing
- Screen size detection and categorization
- Responsive typography scaling
- Image and media responsiveness
- Layout constraint management
- Device-specific optimizations
- Responsive navigation patterns
- Accessibility across screen sizes
- Performance-optimized layouts
- Cross-platform responsiveness

Provides complete responsive design system for building mobile applications
that adapt beautifully to different screen sizes and device capabilities.
:End Note

